This morning he peed on a backpack that was lying on Holly's floor. I was
in

<< definitely not more educational than the cat AND the tennis shoes together!

<<This isn't the cat that taught himself to pee in the toilet by watching is
it? >>

Our cat would more likely pee in the tennis shoe.

This morning he peed on a backpack that was lying on Holly's floor. I was in
there sleeping too. I heard him scratching on it and I threw a slipper at
him. He took off, but came back. Idiot cat.

I'm so glad we have a washing machine.

Sandra
